== Overview ==
The Bulwark is an unusual hybrid design, created by renegade artificial intelligence to combat the CCU in the Vulcore plains. The Bulwark offers shielding abilities similar to a Sentinel, merged with a powerful weapons platform. You have been lucky enough to recreate the technology yourself.

